Below are 4 exact walkthroughs:

- 3 failure-case simulations
- 1 normal success simulation

I’ll keep the same architecture:

- Module 2 decides
- Module 3 executes one requested capability
- Module 3 returns only intermediate decision-requiring events
- final validated output does not go back to Module 2

